{"tid":1953014,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為球王美斯作左首歌","createTime":"2020-04-01T02:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T05:06:55.000Z","uid":199804,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5ddee320648ecd9d9d5c2a6dfd9d4ed0594e57","tid":1953014,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"美洲杯乜鳩都冇我又發狂<br />\n冇事嘅還有競逐世杯<br />\n被法德打到哭了我又退隊<br />\n等到外圍賽歸隊兩年又要走了<br />\n<br />\n還能憑什麼 西甲若未能令我興奮<br />\n原來為國家 捧杯是多麼性感<br />\n還能憑什麼 要是世杯收撚柒皮<br />\n仲有D可能 競逐美洲杯<br />\n<br />\n誰人又相信花是世一這膚淺對白<br />\n來吧要杯嗎 我足總決定年年辦美洲杯<br />\n如從未拎過 因為狂射失penalty<br />\n才令我因你美洲杯每年再再再再搞一搞<br />\n<br />\n今次又輸左 退隊翻幾個月頭<br />\n原來又到 世杯的外圍賽 歸隊返黎是我<br />\n<br />\n我踢足巴塞廿年你別皺眉<br />\n我份約和你繼續至死<br />\n我只想屈喺西甲去做小花<br />\n請你別嫌我不挑戰英超 踢死巴塞<br />\n<br />\n誰人又相信花是世一這膚淺對白<br />\n無謂去挑戰 走出西甲就完全無法適應<br />\n其實有邊個 球員能在多league稱王<br />\n其實有一個 有一位踢齊意甲英超西甲<br />\n<br />\n歐戰遇著對利物浦輕鬆的walk<br />\n領先幾粒也可反cup<br />\n多次十二碼又射失嬲嬲豬囉<br />\n我只可dup低個柒頭 無人及我<br />\n你怎麼竟然說足波之王 是我<br />\n<br />\n我不得不去認同朗是最強 <br />\n吾晚晚丁佢丁得瘋狂射 忘掉我"},{"pid":"e53c81643db7ffee8f9d561efa6d1cb23a9dc6f0","tid":1953014,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">射到</span>忘掉我"},{"pid":"0d1c349f0fe330602ba4c13225432bdad05a698b","tid":1953014,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"林夕？"},{"pid":"7855c1b74358594911762fec2323746f260f3fb8","tid":1953014,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"誰人又相信花是世一這膚淺對白<br />\n來吧要杯嗎 我足總決定年年辦美洲杯<br />\n如從未拎過 因為狂射失penalty<br />\n才令我因你美洲杯每年再再再再搞一搞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5709c314012d05fa580273be67e9e46e280e377d","tid":1953014,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f211cb87f89ec3d5693eefeca18b76aa9327a4c","tid":1953014,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621556d2dc8762d5a24759d4e7b9c22aa05305e7","tid":1953014,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f211cb87f89ec3d5693eefeca18b76aa9327a4c","tid":1953014,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:56:31.000Z","msg":"開左3個po都冇人"},{"pid":"e46257419449b6bb7b2093d1e7291a1b879ad0a7","tid":1953014,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"621556d2dc8762d5a24759d4e7b9c22aa05305e7","tid":1953014,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f211cb87f89ec3d5693eefeca18b76aa9327a4c","tid":1953014,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:39:28.000Z","msg":"想聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T23:56:31.000Z","msg":"開左3個po都冇人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"將標題改牙朗可能呃到人入去"},{"pid":"01eed1949faf6daf1ff0137eaceb5551e01b7646","tid":1953014,"uid":203961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"雖然你好煩膠 不過老實講填得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0813d69bc0b344ac3a54d5b7cb908e8086beafe","tid":1953014,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFqe1Sd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=